                    <bibl><ptr target="#cdl2003"/><citedRange/></bibl>, whence 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>53.2029</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>019900</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><persName type="attested" key="http://clas-lgpn2.classics.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/lgpn_search.cgi?id=V1-65449"><name nymRef="#Πραξιτέλης">Πραξιτέλης</name> <persName type="attested" key="http://clas-lgpn2.classics.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/lgpn_search.cgi?id=V1-64442"><name type="patronymic" nymRef="#Ἰσχέμαχος">Ἰσχεμά<supplied reason="lost">χω</supplied></name></persName></persName>
                    <lb n="2"/><name type="festival" key="Nemea" nymRef="#Νέμεα">Νέμεα</name>
                    <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied>οῖς <w lemma="θεός">θεοῖς</w> τοῖς <w>ἐν</w> τᾶι <w lemma="ἀγορά">ἀγορᾶι</w> <w lemma="ἀνατίθημι">ἀνέθηκ<supplied reason="lost">ε</supplied></w>.

	 </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p/>
 </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Praxitélès fils d'Iskhémakhos, <supplied reason="subaudible">vainqueur aux</supplied> jeux Néméens, a consacré <supplied reason="subaudible">ce monument</supplied> aux dieux de l'agora.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Praxiteles son of Ischemachos, <supplied reason="subaudible">winner at the</supplied> Nemean games, dedicated <supplied reason="subaudible">this monument</supplied> to the gods of the agora.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Praxiteles figlio di Ischemachos, <supplied reason="subaudible">vincitore ai</supplied> giochi di Nemea, ha dedicato <supplied reason="subaudible">questo monumento</supplied> agli dèi dell'agora.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>For the historical context, see <bibl><ptr target="#laronde1987"/></bibl>.</p>
	<p/>
	<p/>
            </div></body>
